dataArray.Name: Iron Ore
dataArray.Description: It is collected from mining the iron veins and used for smelting iron ingots and magnets.

dataArray.Name: Copper Ore
dataArray.Description: It is collected from mining the copper veins and can be smelted directly into copper ingots.

dataArray.Name: Silicon Ore
dataArray.Description: It is a high-purity silicon ore harvested from mining the silicon veins. It is used to make high-purity silicon.

dataArray.Name: Titanium Ore
dataArray.Description: It is a type of ore with a unique molecular structure created under intense heat.

dataArray.Name: Stone
dataArray.Description: It is a common type of ore and an important raw material for production. It can also be harvested from rocks.

dataArray.Name: Coal
dataArray.Description: It is a solid combustible ore. It is gradually formed by plants through complex physiological and bio-mechanical changes. It is an energy source and a vital raw material for smelting and chemical production.

dataArray.Name: Log
dataArray.Description: It is a normal fuel that has a lower energy and is collected from trees,

dataArray.Name: Plant Fuel
dataArray.Description: It contains lower energy compared to wood, but it is easier to harvest.

dataArray.Name: Fire Ice
dataArray.Description: It is a rare ore and an ice-like white solid matter having cage-like micro-structures. Its covalent bonds are at a critical state, which make them the ideal material for more efficient graphene production.

dataArray.Name: Kimberlite Ore
dataArray.Description: It is a rare ore formed and crystallized directly from kimberlite magmas under COâ-rich conditions. Smelting it yield diamonds.

dataArray.Name: Fractal Silicon
dataArray.Description: It is a rare natural silicon ore with a unique geometric fractal structure. When a single crystal grows to a certain size, it is notable that a small twig of silicon crystals grow out of the matrix. Crystal fractalization is a natural occurring process. The higher in fractal generations, the greater in purity. Fractal silicon with more than six fractal generations can be used directly as a raw material for producing crystal silicon.

dataArray.Name: Grating Crystal
dataArray.Description: It is a rare ore with naturally formed grooves distributed across the surface. It is used to produce precision optical components and high-power exciters.

dataArray.Name: Stalagmite Crystal
dataArray.Description: They were rare creatures that once widely existed on this living planet in the ocean at a depth of 100,000 meters. After the marine life on these planets die, their bodies sink to the bottom of the ocean, and mineralize with seawater under the deep pressure of the ocean. If there is a stable, smooth, slow and hot ocean current, stalagmite crystals may form as a result of this occurrence.

dataArray.Name: Unipolar Magnet
dataArray.Description: It is a rare ore with a pyrochlore lattice. In order to separate the "magnetic monopoles", a magnetic field can be applied to affect the symmetry and orientation of the string by lowering the density of the string network.

dataArray.Name: Iron Ingot
dataArray.Description: It is a basic raw material used to produce various iron components.

dataArray.Name: Copper Ingot
dataArray.Description: It is a basic raw material used to produce various copper components.

dataArray.Name: High-purity Silicon
dataArray.Description: After melting and re-crystallization of the crude silicon, analytically pure silicon crystals are formed. The photovoltaic materials and semiconductor components made from them can fulfill a variety of needs.

dataArray.Name: Titanium Ingot
dataArray.Description: Obtained from smelting titanium ores, it is light in weight and highly dense, making it an essential raw material for producing high-density materials.

dataArray.Name: Stone Brick
dataArray.Description: It is a common material obtained by smelting stones and used to produce the foundation of the facilities.

dataArray.Name: Energetic Graphite
dataArray.Description: Impurities such as hydrogen in coal is directly removed from the ion current, followed by a compaction process to yield crystalline graphite that has superior application performance.

dataArray.Name: Steel
dataArray.Description: Iron ingots as raw materials are smelted under strict temperature control to improve the crystal structure of the materials, and yield a higher mechanical properties.

dataArray.Name: Titanium Alloy
dataArray.Description: Utilizing the uniqueness of the lattice structure in titanium at different temperatures, adding precise and proportional amount of alloying elements can achieve the perfect balance of phase transition temperature and phase content, resulting a new type of alloy material with superior strength and density.

dataArray.Name: Glass
dataArray.Description: It is an irregularly structured amorphous optical medium. It can be used to make various optical components such as prisms and lenses, and it can also be used to build a variety of facilities.

dataArray.Name: Titanium Glass
dataArray.Description: Blending a proportional amount of titanium into molten glass can greatly strengthen the glass to withstand hostile environments.

dataArray.Name: Prism
dataArray.Description: It is a polyhedron surrounded by two intersecting glass planes. It splits light or disperses light beams, making it a key component for producing more precise optical instruments.

dataArray.Name: Diamond
dataArray.Description: Diamonds are formed by using extreme high pressure and heat to alter the structure of graphite. Not only does it preserve the parallel hexagonal lattice of graphite but also form a cubic hexagonal lattice, and it is a very hard crystal.

dataArray.Name: Crystal Silicon
dataArray.Description: Melting high-purity silicon and passing it through a strong electric field at a certain speed will yield a spectrally pure silicon crystal. This process can further remove any dissolved ionic impurities. Lattice silicon is almost free of crystal defects, and so it is primarily used to produce ultra-high-precision optical instruments.

dataArray.Name: Gear
dataArray.Description: It is a standard component deployed in a wide range of mechanical structures and used for transmission and other functions.

dataArray.Name: Magnet
dataArray.Description: It is a basic magnetic material obtained directly by smelting iron ores.

dataArray.Name: Magnetic Coil
dataArray.Description: It is an extremely useful basic electromagnetic component.

dataArray.Name: Electric Motor
dataArray.Description: It is a basic power system component that can improve mechanical performance.

dataArray.Name: Electromagnetic Turbine
dataArray.Description: It can defy gravity to levitate objects and is commonly used to create more advanced magnetic field generators.

dataArray.Name: Super-magnetic Ring
dataArray.Description: It is a device to generate super magnetic fields. The resulting super-strong magnetic fields can work at the atomic scale directly and cause distortions in the material lattice, creating high-performance materials and devices.

dataArray.Name: Particle Container
dataArray.Description: It can cause particles to exhibit specific characteristics while firmly binding them.

dataArray.Name: Strange Matter
dataArray.Description: Strange Matter carries great negative gravitational pressure that outweighs its energy density. This allows the space around it to warp and generates negative energy that the warp drive needs.

dataArray.Name: Circuit Board
dataArray.Description: It is a highly versatile basic electrical component.

dataArray.Name: Processor
dataArray.Description: It is a large-scale integrated circuit device. Using semiconductor materials enables better data processing and processing control.

dataArray.Name: Quantum Chip
dataArray.Description: With robust computing power and ultra-fast computation, it can predict if a quantum jump would cause an error and prevent it by promptly reversing a jump process that may result in an error.

dataArray.Name: Microcrystalline Component
dataArray.Description: It is a microcrystalline component, which is the basis for achieving high-speed computing functions in processors. Its production involves carving and fabricating "city-like" three-dimensional nanostructures on high-purity silicon wafers.

dataArray.Name: Plane Filter
dataArray.Description: Studying the probability oscillation in time with the Rabi frequency as the particle wave function evolves makes it possible to artificially interfere with it during a quantum jump to steer the quantum in the desired direction.

dataArray.Name: Particle Broadband
dataArray.Description: Controlling the particles so that they maintain a certain regularity significantly increases the printing speed of the particles.

dataArray.Name: Plasma Exciter
dataArray.Description: The plasma generated by the high-power Plasma Exciter can be used to extract and refine crude oil or create wireless power towers for remote power transmission and charging the mecha.

dataArray.Name: Photon Combiner
dataArray.Description: The prism surface is cut into nano-gratings and then reassembled so that a single high-energy photon is emitted after continuously absorbing multiple low-energy photons in a specific combination of structures. Amazingly, the natural Grating Crystals within the cluster can accomplish this directly.

dataArray.Name: Solar Sail
dataArray.Description: The EM-Rail Ejector can launch large numbers of Solar Sails to create a Dyson Swarm, enabling more efficient radiant energy acquisition from a star.

dataArray.Name: Water
dataArray.Description: It is obtained from using the Water Pump, widely used in chemical production. It can also be used as throwable item to practice but it has no damage or effect.

dataArray.Name: Crude Oil
dataArray.Description: It is a type of fossil formed from marine organisms and can be mined as a liquid mineral. It contains chemical energy stored within marine organisms during their life-time, and can be used as fuel or as a raw chemical material.

dataArray.Name: Refined Oil
dataArray.Description: It is a primary product of crude oil refining. It is a chemical fuel used to manufacture various chemical products.

dataArray.Name: Sulfuric Acid
dataArray.Description: It is a primary chemical product of crude oil. It can be directly obtained from the sulfuric acid ocean using a water pump.

dataArray.Name: Hydrogen
dataArray.Description: The most abundant element in the universe and the lightest gas.

dataArray.Name: Deuterium
dataArray.Description: It is a stable isotope of hydrogen. Rarely found under natural conditions, most of them are from reprocessed hydrogen, or collected from the gas giants.

dataArray.Name: Antimatter
dataArray.Description: It is generated by inverting photons at a critical state. When Matter and Antimatter meet, they annihilate each other, and produce a massive burst of energy.

dataArray.Name: Critical Photon
dataArray.Description: It is a critical state photon that can be converted into Antimatter and hydrogen under the effect of a super magnetic field.

dataArray.Name: Hydrogen Fuel Rod
dataArray.Description: Due to the improvement of cryogenic technology, gaseous hydrogen can condense itself into a fluid to make liquid hydrogen fuel rods with a higher combustion efficiency. Using it as a fuel for the mecha can dramatically improve its combustion output.

dataArray.Name: Deuteron Fuel Rod
dataArray.Description: Under a magnetic field, deuterium can be made into deuteron fuel rods that can yield more powerful energy. These can be used as a fuel source for small fusion systems.

dataArray.Name: Antimatter Fuel Rod
dataArray.Description: The Annihilation Constraint Sphereâs strong restraints act on Antimatter to form a more stable fuel rod. This powerful energy is then safer to harness.

dataArray.Name: Strange Annihilation Fuel Rod
dataArray.Description: If Strange Matter is used as the main raw material for the annihilation reaction, both the energy density and the output power will rise significantly.

dataArray.Name: Plastic
dataArray.Description: It is a primary chemical product, which is highly versatile. It is used to make more advanced chemical products.

dataArray.Name: Graphene
dataArray.Description: If one layer of graphene is laid on top of another layer of graphene, through rotation, the double-layer graphene will form a complex repeating structure - a superlattice. Upon rotation to a certain "Magic Angle", the double-layer graphene will become superconductive and become a new type of nano-superconducting material.

dataArray.Name: Carbon Nanotube
dataArray.Description: It is very lightweight, and has a precisely interconnected hexagonal lattice structure. Such structure imparts exceptional strength and an impressive resistance to deformation, so it is ideally suited for the production of high-performance apparatuses.

dataArray.Name: Organic Crystal
dataArray.Description: It is a high-graded chemical product of crude oil with crystal structure. It can also be sourced directly from rare organic crystal veins, and it is used to produce crystals with higher density.

dataArray.Name: Titanium Crystal
dataArray.Description: Adding precise, proportional organic crystals in titanium can further strengthen its lattice structure, forming special titanium atomic crystals with greater density.

dataArray.Name: Casimir Crystal
dataArray.Description: The ion trapâs electric field holds charged particles in place, and Coulomb repulsion between the particles causes them to spontaneously form a spatial ring crystal. The zero-point energy of the particles inside the crystal can be stimulated by imposing a weak static magnetic field, resulting in a noticeable Casimir effect.

dataArray.Name: Combustible Unit
dataArray.Description: As a fuel, it can efficiently combust and generate enormous energy, while as an explosive component it can be used to craft shells and Explosive Units.

dataArray.Name: Explosive Unit
dataArray.Description: It is a powerful explosive crafted from Combustible Units. Sophisticated design and strict production control will ensure its optimal explosive capacity and stability. As a raw material used in the making of High-explosive Shell Sets, it offers powerful explosiveness and the ability to inflict heavy damage.

dataArray.Name: Crystal Explosive Unit
dataArray.Description: By inducing resonance of Casimir Crystals, its explosiveness is tremendously enhanced by a chainreaction-like effect in a small range.

dataArray.Name: Graviton Lens
dataArray.Description: It is a piece of neutron star material encapsulated after processing. Its distorted and powerful gravitational field is shielded within. It is normally used to manipulate and change the spatial structure, but this does not stop some folks from using it to focus the sunâs rays and ignite a fire.

dataArray.Name: Space Warper
dataArray.Description: It is a consumable item that activates warp flight for the mecha and Logistics Vessels.\r\nUse the <color="#FD965ECC">CAPSLOCK</color> key to activate the warp drive.

dataArray.Name: Annihilation Constraint Sphere
dataArray.Description: Confining the annihilation reaction within the sphere to obtain a stable and controlled energy output is a key component of Artificial Stars.

dataArray.Name: Engine
dataArray.Description: A small aerodynamic component, used as basic part in many aircrafts. This engine can be crafted easily from cheap raw materials.

dataArray.Name: Thruster
dataArray.Description: It can supply power to the Logistics Drones.

dataArray.Name: Reinforced Thruster
dataArray.Description: It is an upgraded version of the thruster that can power the Logistics Vessel.

dataArray.Name: Logistics Bot
dataArray.Description: It actively balances the supply and demand of items in the distribution logistics system, but it will not deliver to destinations beyond the distribution scope.

dataArray.Name: Logistics Drone
dataArray.Description: It functions to dynamically balance the supply and demand of items in the planetary logistics system. It only works with the Logistics Station it comes from.

dataArray.Name: Interstellar Logistics Vessel
dataArray.Description: It functions to actively balance the supply and demand of items between planets. Consuming Space Warpers can enable Logistics Vessels to launch warp flights.

dataArray.Name: Frame Material
dataArray.Description: It is a new type of high-density, lightweight structure. It is more resistant to the strong gravitational pull of stars than traditional structural materials, making it ideal for building Dyson Sphere components.

dataArray.Name: Dyson Sphere Component
dataArray.Description: Small Carrier Rockets can transport the components to the planned Dyson Sphere, where they will form the Dyson Sphereâs Nodes and Frames.

dataArray.Name: Small Carrier Rocket
dataArray.Description: The delivery vehicle for Dyson Sphere Components. More rockets should be launched if a Dyson Sphere needs to be built faster.

dataArray.Name: Foundation
dataArray.Description: It is a terrain leveling tool. But it canât be used to alter the planet's topography. You can only level the terrain to zero elevation. If the foundation is used for highlands, soil piles will be obtained. However, if the foundation is used for ocean or low-lying areas, soil piles will be consumed. When laying the Foundation, you can choose a decoration option or leave it plain and just level the terrain.

dataArray.Name: Proliferator Mk.I
dataArray.Description: Proliferator is input into the port above the Spray Coater and sprayed on cargo. When the sprayed cargo is used as raw materials to make the next-level products, it can yield extra products or speed up production. However, it will increase the power consumption for the entire production process.

dataArray.Name: Proliferator Mk.II
dataArray.Description: Compared to Proliferator MK.I, the Proliferator MK.II ingredient formula is upgraded. When cargo sprayed with Proliferator MK.II is used as raw materials to produce the next-level products, the extra products or production speedup effect can be dramatically improved.

dataArray.Name: Proliferator Mk.III
dataArray.Description: With a newly upgraded formula, when cargo sprayed with Proliferator MK.III is used as raw materials to produce the next-level products, it can help maximize the extra products or production speedup effect. However, the power consumption will increase during the production process, and it requires a higher-capacity production line.

dataArray.Name: Magnum Ammo Box
dataArray.Description: Magnum ammo crafted from copper ingots at low cost. Copper is self-lubricating, so it can maintain its shape and still reduce the risks of deformation and fracturing when shooting. An ammo box contains 30 bullets.

dataArray.Name: Titanium Ammo Box
dataArray.Description: Magnum Ammo Boxes improved with titanium ingots. Now their sharper warheads can pierce Dark Fog's armor easily. An ammo box contains 30 bullets.

dataArray.Name: Superalloy Ammo Box
dataArray.Description: Magnum Ammo Boxs enhanced with titanium alloy. The shape and structure of their cases are modified based on a lightweight titanium alloy, resulting in a higher initial speed, stabler flight capability, and greater power. An ammo box contains 30 bullets.

dataArray.Name: Shell Set
dataArray.Description: Basic shells contain efficient Combustible Units. Once shot to a target position, they will explode immediately and inflict Kinetic and Explosive Damage in the area. A Shell Set contains 12 shells.

dataArray.Name: High-Explosive Shell Set
dataArray.Description: Advanced high-energy Explosive Unit technology powerfully enhances shells. A Shell Set contains 12 shells.

dataArray.Name: Crystal Shell Set
dataArray.Description: Crystal Explosive Units release greater energy with a more powerful smashing effect, inflicting considerable damage to even the toughest enemy units. A Shell Set contains 12 shells.

dataArray.Name: Plasma Capsule
dataArray.Description: Filled with deuterium that, when stimulated by a Plasma Turret, can transform into a high-temperature plasmoid to effectively damage space targets. Each capsule can be stimulated 10 times.

dataArray.Name: Antimatter Capsule
dataArray.Description: The ultimate energy weapon that was once prohibited by COSMO. The target is destroyed instantly due to the enormous amount of energy generated from the annihilation reaction as matter and antimatter collide. Each capsule can be stimulated 10 times.

dataArray.Name: Missile Set
dataArray.Description: The target identification system on the head can adjust its attack trajectory in real time during flight to hit targets. A Missile Set contains 24 missiles.

dataArray.Name: Supersonic Missile Set
dataArray.Description: The thruster's dynamism massively accelerates the missile beyond the speed of sound and the upgraded warhead and payload recipe increases the damage. A Missile Set contains 24 missiles.

dataArray.Name: Gravity Missile Set
dataArray.Description: Strange Matter's negative gravitational pressure is used to warp the surrounding space, thus increasing missile speed. The warping space increases explosive damage. A Missile Set contains 24 missiles.

dataArray.Name: Jamming Capsule
dataArray.Description: A Jammer Tower can interfere with the enemies within the range by consuming Jamming Capsule, reducing their movement speed and rate of fire. Each Jamming Capsule can interfere with 180 units.

dataArray.Name: Suppressing Capsule
dataArray.Description: Suppressing Capsule can slow down even suppress enemies, preventing them from attacking. Each Suppressing Capsule can interfere with 180 units.

dataArray.Name: Prototype
dataArray.Description: Ground forces, prototypes of Combat Drones, that can assist Icarus in fights on planet surfaces. Though simple and crude, it represents a decent start. You can get a better Combat Drone by modifying and upgrading the prototype.\r\n\r\nNote: Ground fighters cannot be deployed in space!

dataArray.Name: Precision Drone
dataArray.Description: Ground forces, which can assist Icarus in fights on planet surfaces. Based on a prototype and with a built-in Photon Combiner, it can continuously absorb low-energy photons and convert them to high-energy ones. This type of laser weapon can accurately hit and damage targets without needing to be near them. It is suitable for assaulting distant enemy units.\r\n\r\nNote: Ground fighters cannot be deployed in space!

dataArray.Name: Attack Drone
dataArray.Description: Ground forces, which can assist Icarus in fights on planet surfaces. Based on a prototype and with a stronger, built-in EM weapon system, it can only attack close targets. You can enhance its survival capabilities by upgrading its armor.\r\n\r\nNote: Ground fighters cannot be deployed in space!

dataArray.Name: Corvette
dataArray.Description: Space forces, which consist of small vessels, that can assist Icarus in fights in space and hit distant targets.

dataArray.Name: Destroyer
dataArray.Description: Space forces which consist of medium Warships. Destroyers are larger and more aggressive. They are used to attack enemy units nearby and exert a more suppressive and destructive effect. It costs 4 Command Pts to command a Destroyer. This means a Space Fleet can only have a maximum of 3 Destroyers at a time.

dataArray.Name: Dark Fog Matrix
dataArray.Description: A mystery substance collected from Dark Fog Debris. Deep scanning reveals that this substance has a topological structure that we have never seen before. Vaguely familiar yet also different, it appears to contain unusual information. We might be able to obtain something different by solving the mystery that surrounds it.

dataArray.Name: Silicon-based Neuron
dataArray.Description: Obtained from Dark Fog Debris. These silicon-based neurons have both storage and computing capabilities. When several silicon-based neurons are combined, they can simulate the brain operation of a carbon-based life form.

dataArray.Name: Matter Recombinator
dataArray.Description: Obtained from Dark Fog Debris. Research reveals that this substance has powerful decomposing and re-composing capabilities. It can instantly decompose matter into particles, and then re-compose these particles as designed to generate a different type of matter.\r\n

dataArray.Name: Negentropy Singularity
dataArray.Description: Initial experiments hadn't identified any special properties of the substance. Yet when we keep inputting energy, it spontaneously shows weak negentropy.

dataArray.Name: Core Element
dataArray.Description: A Core Element is a novel type of matter which can be found in the debris of advanced Dark Fog. It has been discovered in experiments that a Core Element can efficiently and spontaneously combine itself with other types of matter, but it can't be singularized by Strange Matter. Therefore, adding a Core Element to the singularization reaction of Strange Matter can slow down that reaction and make it more orderly.

dataArray.Name: Energy Shard
dataArray.Description: A chemical fuel obtained from Dark Fog Debris. When providing energy to Icarus, its internal molecular stimulation mechanism can accelerate the speed of the Replicator.

dataArray.Name: Conveyor Belt MK.I
dataArray.Description: We need automation! Conveyor Belts are the most basic components of automated production. They can transport cargo from one location to another.

dataArray.Name: Conveyor Belt MK.II
dataArray.Description: This Conveyor Belt type allows for faster cargo transportation and has higher throughput.

dataArray.Name: Conveyor Belt MK.III
dataArray.Description: It can maximize the speed and throughput of transported cargo.

dataArray.Name: Sorter MK.I
dataArray.Description: It can transport cargo into a facility via Conveyor Belts, or between facilities. Filters can be configured to filter the cargo.

dataArray.Name: Sorter MK.II
dataArray.Description: It enables faster cargo picking and sorting.

dataArray.Name: Sorter MK.III
dataArray.Description: It can maximize cargo sorting speed. A Sorter Mk.III at maximum cycle speed can satisfy a Conveyor Belt.

dataArray.Name: Pile Sorter
dataArray.Description: After upgrading it, the Pile Sorter can integrate multiple cargos into one and feed out it. Even it is slightly expensive but it is a good deal for those engineers who are dedicated to run the Conveyor Belt at full speed.

dataArray.Name: Splitter
dataArray.Description: It is designed to distribute cargo to different Conveyor Belts or balance out multiple Conveyor Belts. Filters and infeed/outfeed priority can be set on any port.

dataArray.Name: Automatic Piler
dataArray.Description: Building an Auto-piler on a Conveyor Belt automatically merges two cargoes on the belt into one, which significantly enhances the belt's carrying capacity.

dataArray.Name: Traffic Monitor
dataArray.Description: Building a Flow Meter on a Conveyor Belt monitors the real-time flow rate at a corresponding location on the belt. Criteria can be specified to trigger an alarm.

dataArray.Name: Spray Coater
dataArray.Description: Fitting the Spray Coater to a Conveyor Belt and feeding it to the Proliferator through the upper port allows cargo on the Conveyor Belt to be sprayed. Production is either accelerated or extra products gained when cargo sprayed with the Proliferator is used as raw material to create next-level products.

dataArray.Name: Logistics Distributor
dataArray.Description: After the Logistics Distributor is installed on the top floor of a Depot, the Logistics Bot will automatically deliver the Depot's contents to Icarus' Inventory or other Logistics Distributors. This greatly helps Icarus to access various items in a short distance.

dataArray.Name: Depot MK.I
dataArray.Description: Storage space for products, although its capacity is limited.

dataArray.Name: Depot MK.II
dataArray.Description: It has double the capacity of a Depot Mk.I, but requires steel to produce.

dataArray.Name: Storage Tank
dataArray.Description: Storage Tank has a larger capacity for containing fluids than a Depot.

dataArray.Name: Assembling Machine Mk.I
dataArray.Description: The basic assembler can transform primary items such as iron and copper ingots into more advanced products.

dataArray.Name: Assembling Machine Mk.II
dataArray.Description: With significantly improved production speed, items can be produced more quickly.

dataArray.Name: Assembling Machine Mk.III
dataArray.Description: It maximizes the production speed. Conveyor Belts and Sorters of different speeds can be combined to avoid empty assemblers or product overflow.

dataArray.Name: Re-composing Assembler
dataArray.Description: The AI module can analyze the recipe of an item in real time and decompose raw materials into particles by precisely controlling the structure and compound mode of molecules. After that, it then re-composes particles to form required items and performs Quantum Printing, greatly improving manufacturing speed.

dataArray.Name: Tesla Tower
dataArray.Description: It is a power transmission facility with a particular connection length and coverage that can extend the supply range of the Power Grid.

dataArray.Name: Wireless Power Tower
dataArray.Description: It is a remote power transmission facility that can draw electricity from the Power Grid and charge the mecha.

dataArray.Name: Satellite Substation
dataArray.Description: It is a wide-area distribution facility capable of transmitting power over a longer range, thereby enabling broader coverage.

dataArray.Name: Wind Turbine
dataArray.Description: It is a primary power generator that converts wind energy into electrical energy. The actual power generation performance depends on the planetâs wind energy utilization.

dataArray.Name: Thermal Power Plant
dataArray.Description: It is a facility that generates electricity using combustible materials, such as coal, as fuel. The energy output to heat generation ratio depends on the fuel consumption.

dataArray.Name: Mini Fusion Power Plant
dataArray.Description: Under the effect of a high-intensity, high-density magnetic field, this facility can turn the enormous energy emitted by Deuteron Fuel Rods via a controlled fusion reaction into electricity.

dataArray.Name: Geothermal Power Station
dataArray.Description: It is a power generation facility fueled by magma, where multiple successive low-energy photons are merged into a single high-energy photon and the energy is steadily transmitted to the Power Grid. The generation output directly correlates to the concentration of magma.

dataArray.Name: Mining Machine
dataArray.Description: The more ore veins covered by a Mining Machine, the faster the extraction speed. Multiple Mining Rings can cover the same vein, but the more Mining Rings covering a vein, the faster the loss.

dataArray.Name: Advanced Mining Machine
dataArray.Description: The Quantum Chip is used to manipulate the photon groups generated by the Exciter during the quantum jump process, causing the laser beam to focus intensely. The focused laser beam rapidly heats the ore veins along a predetermined path in a special gravitational field. If ores are transported and contained in particle form, building is easier and ores are collected faster. The collected ores can be shipped out by Conveyor Belts or Logistics Drones.

dataArray.Name: Water Pump
dataArray.Description: It is a facility that pumps liquids directly from oceans, including the sulfuric acid ocean.

dataArray.Name: Arc Smelter
dataArray.Description: It smelts ores and metals at high temperatures generated by the electrode arc and is also useful for purification and crystal smelting.

dataArray.Name: Plane Smelter
dataArray.Description: When magnetic monopoles travel through the Plane Filter, they generate quantum effects, which can produce thermodynamic negative temperature flow. Ores can be smelted or purified at accelerated rates using this principle.

dataArray.Name: Negentropy Smelter
dataArray.Description: After energy has been put in continuously, the stimulated negentropy singularity in the Smelter can steadily give off negentropy. Despite the fact that little negentropy is obtained, after being repeated and repeated the process can efficiently restore ores to their elemental states from impure ones.

dataArray.Name: Oil Extractor
dataArray.Description: It uses focusing plasma to extract crude oil from oil seeps. The extraction speed is dependent on the yield of the oil seep and the level of Resource Utilization.

dataArray.Name: Oil Refinery
dataArray.Description: Refined oil and hydrogen are obtained by further refining extracted crude oil.

dataArray.Name: Chemical Plant
dataArray.Description: It is a chemical production facility that can process the primary products of crude oil into more advanced chemical products.

dataArray.Name: Quantum Chemical Plant
dataArray.Description: Quantum entanglement formed via Strange Matter at specific points could decouple the most complicated part of the chaos phenomenon in chemical reactions. This may lead the reactions toward a predetermined direction. If these magic points could evolve, they could catalyze the corresponding chemical reactions.

dataArray.Name: Fractionator
dataArray.Description: Deuterium can be fractionated from liquid hydrogen efficiently by utilizing the high vapor pressure ratio of liquid hydrogen to liquid deuterium at a certain temperature. A Conveyor Belt is used to import hydrogen from one side. After fractionation, the hydrogen will be exported from the other side, and the fractionated deuterium will be exported from the front port.

dataArray.Name: Solar Panel
dataArray.Description: It generates electricity from sunlight. The actual power generation performance is linked with the planetâs light energy utilization. Stops running at night. Accumulators can be used to store surplus electricity during the day.

dataArray.Name: Accumulator
dataArray.Description: It is an electric power storage device. When surplus power is available in the Power Grid, excess power will be automatically stored. When the power supply is insufficient, stored power will be automatically released to operate the facility.

dataArray.Name: Accumulator (full)
dataArray.Description: It is an Accumulator with full charge. It can either be used as a facility to automatically release power when the power is insufficient, or it can be placed in an Energy Exchanger to release electricity.

dataArray.Name: EM-Rail Ejector
dataArray.Description: It ejects considerable Solar Sails to integrate with the Dyson Swarm.

dataArray.Name: Ray Receiver
dataArray.Description: It receives high-energy rays transmitted from the Dyson Swarm or Dyson Sphere. The received energy can be transmitted directly to the Power Grid or stored as Critical Photons.

dataArray.Name: Vertical Launching Silo
dataArray.Description: It launches Small Carrier Rockets carrying components into the Dyson Sphere orbit to form Nodes and Frames.

dataArray.Name: Energy Exchanger
dataArray.Description: It is a facility that can convert electric power. It can either deposit surplus power from the Power Grid into an empty Accumulator to fully charge it, or release the power stored in a fully charged Accumulator.

dataArray.Name: Miniature Particle Collider
dataArray.Description: New particles can be produced when two streams of accelerated particles, upon reaching a certain intensity and energy, collide. It is usually employed to create stable deuterium and antimatter, but consumes considerable energy.

dataArray.Name: Artificial Star
dataArray.Description: "Just allow the positive and negative proton beams to pass silently through the magnetic field from both ends into the Constraint Sphere, nice and easy!" It is simple but effective and is called the Artificial Sun.

dataArray.Name: Planetary Logistics Station
dataArray.Description: It is the hub of the planetary logistics system. Logistics Drones will automatically deliver the cargo to the respective stations once you have specified the supply/demand requirements.\r\n(Transportation is limited to its own planet)

dataArray.Name: Interstellar Logistics Station
dataArray.Description: Giant space elevators make it easier to transport materials between planets. They can connect factories on different planets to form a massive industrial empire.

dataArray.Name: Orbital Collector
dataArray.Description: It is used to collect resources from gas giants. It needs to consume the collected fuel materials to power the collector to work in orbit.

dataArray.Name: Matrix Lab
dataArray.Description: It is a type of connector for the CentreBrain, which can either produce matrices or conduct research. The more Matrix Labs, the faster the production and research speeds.

dataArray.Name: Self-evolution Lab
dataArray.Description: A Self-evolution Lab allows silicon-based neurons to autonomously adjust and improve neural networking while constantly learning and adapting, similar to the synaptic plasticity of biological neurons. Over time, silicon-based neurons can keep optimizing their own structures and function through self-evolution to solve problems more effectively.

dataArray.Name: Gauss Turret
dataArray.Description: An EM field is used to accelerate bullet speed. 48mm bullets form dense and intense firepower. The damage inflicted to low-air units as a result should not be underestimated.

dataArray.Name: Laser Turret
dataArray.Description: High-energy laser beams will be emitted to keep strafing enemy units when they enter the defensive range. High temperatures lead to sustained damage to targets. Laser Towers' high-frequency lasers can hit targets precisely and in a short period of time, but they consume a lot of energy.

dataArray.Name: Implosion Cannon
dataArray.Description: After hitting a target, a 280mm shell can cause a wide-ranging explosive blast and inflict Explosive Damage to units and facilities in the vicinity. Additionally, due to its design characteristics Implosion Cannon can't be used to attack close targets.

dataArray.Name: Plasma Turret
dataArray.Description: After being stimulated, the matter inside an energy capsule will be in a high-energy plasma state. It will then be quickly emitted by the Plasma Turret's accelerator to generate high-speed plasma beams. Such beams are extremely penetrating and destructive, and can effectively destroy space targets.

dataArray.Name: Missile Turret
dataArray.Description: Equipped with an advanced missile launcher and a target identification system, Turrets can quickly identify and locate both ground and space targets. Once they lock onto a target, they will then launch missiles. They are designed to respond to multiple threats with all-around defense.

dataArray.Name: Jammer Tower
dataArray.Description: It can interfere with nearby enemy units periodically, decreasing their movement speed and rate of fire. Each interference consumes EM capsule once.

dataArray.Name: Signal Tower
dataArray.Description: A tactical defensive facility that periodically sends out signals at a specific frequency to induce Dark Fog, change the direction of an attack and increase the unit assembling speed. Signal Towers can form a data chain with Missile Turrets for information sharing, thus expanding the attack range of Missile Turrets.

dataArray.Name: Planetary Shield Generator
dataArray.Description: They can create Planetary Shields on planets to resist attacks from space. Massive amounts of energy are required for a Planetary Shield. If the shield becomes ineffective, it will leave the planet exposed to serious threats from space. Additionally, the number of Shield Generators that can be built on a planet is limited.\r\nPlanetary Shield can only resist damage from space, it cannot defend ground damage.

dataArray.Name: Battlefield Analysis Base
dataArray.Description: The core for battlefield controlling with powerful real-time battlefield analysis and command capabilities. Self-equipped Fighters can be dispatched for base defense. A destroyed building will automatically be marked with a hologram. Construction Drones will then be dispatched for building and repair to provide support on the battlefield. A Battlefield Analysis Base can also collect enemy debris for analysis and acquire useful intelligence and resources from battlefield residues.

dataArray.Name: SR Plasma Turret
dataArray.Description: The powerful high-temperature plasma can melt enemies within its range, but maintaining such a device on the ground is not easy. To be able to attack nearby targets, constantly maintaining the excited plasma makes this facility very fragile and requires a large amount of power.

dataArray.Name: Electromagnetic Matrix
dataArray.Description: The foundation of all technological research as one of the five basic source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation.

dataArray.Name: Energy Matrix
dataArray.Description: The Energy Matrix is a major driver of further technological development as one of the five basic source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation.

dataArray.Name: Structure Matrix
dataArray.Description: Useful for obtaining new and improved structural materials as one of the five basic source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation.

dataArray.Name: Information Matrix
dataArray.Description: One of the five basic source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation. The level of computerization significantly affects how well the Homebase operates.

dataArray.Name: Gravity Matrix
dataArray.Description: One of the five basic source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation. It finds a way to make quantum field theory and general relativity compatible.

dataArray.Name: Universe Matrix
dataArray.Description: The triumphant, all-encompassing culmination of the theory of everything, revealing the ultimate secret of the universe!

dataArray.Name: Plasma Refining
dataArray.Description: Refine crude oil with plasma to obtain hydrogen and refined oil.

dataArray.Name: Casimir Crystal (advanced)
dataArray.Description: The utilization of the rare Grating Crystal for the production of Casimir Crystal results in significantly enhanced efficiency.

dataArray.Name: Graphene (advanced)
dataArray.Description: Fire Ice Vein would greatly facilitate the production of graphene.

dataArray.Name: Carbon Nanotube (advanced)
dataArray.Description: It is feasible to produce Carbon Nanotubes using Stalagmite Crystal, however, this ore is quite rare and difficult to locate.

dataArray.Name: Organic Crystal (original)
dataArray.Description: The processing of wood, plant fuel, and water resources yields Organic Crystal.

dataArray.Name: X-ray Cracking
dataArray.Description: Through the catalytic action of hydrogen gas, the refined oil is subjected to X-ray irradiation, leading to its cracking and yielding an increased quantity of hydrogen, as well as a byproduct: Energetic Graphite.

dataArray.Name: Diamond (advanced)
dataArray.Description: Find Kimberlite Ore and you can smelt it to produce diamonds.

dataArray.Name: Crystal Silicon (advanced)
dataArray.Description: The unique fractal structure possessed by Fractal Silicon makes it the preferred material for the efficient production of crystal silicon.

dataArray.Name: Photon Combiner (advanced)
dataArray.Description: The discovery of Grating Crystal would facilitate the production of Photon Combiner.

dataArray.Name: Mass-energy Storage
dataArray.Description: Under the influence of an intense magnetic field, Critical Photons can be converted into Antimatter and hydrogen.

dataArray.Name: Space Warper (advanced)
dataArray.Description: The existence of Gravity Matrix facilitates the production of Space Warpers.

dataArray.Name: Particle Container (advanced)
dataArray.Description: While Unipolar Magnets are exceedingly rare, their discovery would enable more efficient production of Particle Containers.

dataArray.Name: Deuterium Fractionation
dataArray.Description: The successful fractionation of deuterium from liquid hydrogen has greatly advanced the utilization of nuclear fuel.

dataArray.Name: Reformed Refinement
dataArray.Description: By adding hydrogen and coal to refined oil and subjecting it to a process of reformation, a greater quantity of refined oil can be produced.

dataArray.Name: Dyson Sphere Program
dataArray.Desc: Welcome to the Dyson Sphere Program!\r\nYou will establish a giant intergalactic industrial empire from scratch, and carve out your own path to a miracle of the universe, the Dyson Sphere.

dataArray.Name: Electromagnetism
dataArray.Desc: The poetic Maxwell's equations showcased to the world the relationship between electricity and magnetism. Based on a profound understanding of these knowledge, efficient machines for acquiring and utilizing electrical energy have been created.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked a new type of automatic mining machine. It performs automatic mining ore for you. Its capacity is limited, so you might want to automatically deliver ores to the smelters.

dataArray.Name: Electromagnetic Matrix
dataArray.Desc: The Electromagnetic Matrix is the foundation of all technologies as one of the five basic source codes for CentreBrain to maintain Homeland simulation. Upload Electromagnetic Matrices to unlock more technologies.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Matrix Lab! Also called the CentreBrain Connector, it can be used to unlock new technologies by uploading matrices to it.

dataArray.Name: High-Efficiency Plasma Control
dataArray.Desc: The modified Plasma Exciter features improved stability and efficiency due to its more efficient use of plasma via electric and magnetic fields.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Plasma Control technology. You can now build a Wireless Power Tower to transmit electricity remotely and charge the mecha. The next step could be to use this technology as a basis for researching the extraction and refining of crude oil.

dataArray.Name: Plasma Extract Refining
dataArray.Desc: New plasma technology facilitates industrial development by drastically improving crude oil refinement efficiency.
dataArray.Conclusion: You can now extract crude oil, which can not only be used as an energy source but also be refined into various chemical products.

dataArray.Name: X-Ray Cracking
dataArray.Desc: High-energy X-ray photocatalysis produces more hydrogen via the pyrolysis of refined oil. It also produces Energetic Graphite through pyrolysis byproduct processing.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the X-ray Cracking technology. Use it to crack refined oil into hydrogen and gain Energetic Graphite.

dataArray.Name: Reformed Refinement
dataArray.Desc: Breakthroughs in chemical engineering have increased the efficiency of refined oil production by reforming it with hydrogen and coal.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Reformed Refinement technology. Use it to produce more refined oil for producing next-level chemical products.

dataArray.Name: Energy Matrix
dataArray.Desc: Energy Matrix is the key to the source of energy as one of the five basic source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation. Upload Energy Matrices to unlock more energy technologies.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Energy Matrix, a powerful matrix that serves as one of the five source codes for CentreBrain to maintain Homeland simulation, but also the key to accessing more technologies.

dataArray.Name: Hydrogen Fuel Rod
dataArray.Desc: Due to the improvement of cryogenic technology, gaseous hydrogen can condense itself into a fluid to make liquid hydrogen fuel rods with a higher combustion efficiency. Using it as a fuel for the mecha can dramatically improve its combustion output.
dataArray.Conclusion: You have obtained a higher-energy fuel rod. Insert it into the mecha's fuel chamber to increase efficiency and speed up energy recovery.

dataArray.Name: Thruster
dataArray.Desc: A high-efficiency engine that propels Logistics Drones to travel between Planetary Logistics Stations on a planet via the counterforce generated by the high-speed ejection of plasma mass.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Thruster. Use it as a Logistics Drone engine to transport cargo across the planet.

dataArray.Name: Reinforced Thruster
dataArray.Desc: An upgraded engine that propels Logistics Vessels to travel between planets.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Augmented Thruster. Use it as a Logistics Vessel engine to enable interstellar cargo transportation.

dataArray.Name: Fluid Storage Encapsulation
dataArray.Desc: Enables the containerization of fluids for more convenient transportation.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Fluid Encapsulation technology. Use it to deliver fluids via Conveyor Belts and store excess fluids in large-capacity Storage Tanks.

dataArray.Name: Basic Chemical Engineering
dataArray.Desc: Scientific development would have stalled without chemical engineering.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Basic Chemical Engineering technology. Establish Chemical Plants to produce more chemical products.

dataArray.Name: Polymer Chemical Engineering
dataArray.Desc: A new polymer synthesis technology that processes refined oil and plastic into a new material, Organic Crystal.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Polymer Engineering technology. This allows you to use Chemical Plants to produce Organic Crystal. Although the fuel chamber efficiency is reduced, the mecha can still use Organic Crystal as a source of fuel.

dataArray.Name: High-Strength Crystal
dataArray.Desc: High-strength titanium crystals are obtained by altering the lattice structure of titanium atoms by adding a precise proportion of Organic Crystal.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've learned a method to prepare high-density crystal. The Titanium Crystal, a special kind of titanium atom crystal, can be obtained by altering the lattice structure of titanium atoms with Organic Crystal.

dataArray.Name: Structure Matrix
dataArray.Desc: Structure Matrices are one of the five basic source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation. Uploading Structure Matrices increases expertise on material structures.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Structure Matrix, a type of matrix that is one of the five source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation. Uploading Structure Matrices to the CentreBrain will give you insight into material structures.

dataArray.Name: Casimir Crystal
dataArray.Desc: A ring-shaped space crystal built with a strong electrical field and utilizing the Coulomb repulsion between particles. Using a weak, static magnetic field produces a significant Casimir effect.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Casimir Crystal. Grating Crystal, a rare ore, facilitates the preparation of Casimir Crystal.

dataArray.Name: High-Strength Glass
dataArray.Desc: High-density glass, with higher complexity and density, suitable for industrial manufacturing. It is obtained by adding a set proportion of titanium and Organic Crystal to molten glass.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Titanium Glass, a kind of high-strength glass made from molten glass and a fixed proportion of additive titanium. Titanium Glass can be used in a relatively intense reaction environment.

dataArray.Name: Applied Superconductor
dataArray.Desc: The emergence of graphene is a breakthrough in material technology. Superconductivity can be detected in twisted bilayer graphene at a certain "magic angle".
dataArray.Conclusion: You've obtained graphene, a novel nanoscale superconductor with a broad range of uses. Fire Ice, a rare ore, can greatly improve the efficiency of graphene preparation.

dataArray.Name: High-Strength Material
dataArray.Desc: Harder than diamonds, Carbon Nanotubes are used to manufacture special objects that can maintain structural integrity in high-pressure industrial environments.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've obtained Carbon Nanotube, a material with extraordinarily high strength and resistance to deformation that is harder than diamonds. The preparation of Carbon Nanotubes can be greatly facilitated by Stalagmite Crystal, a rare ore that can be found on marine planets.

dataArray.Name: Particle Control
dataArray.Desc: Mastering Particle Manipulation technology is greatly beneficial despite its profundity and complexity. Particle Manipulation is much easier once the particle structure adopts a pattern under certain conditions.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Particle Manipulation technology. Use it to impose a specific pattern on the movement of particles.

dataArray.Name: Deuterium Fractionation
dataArray.Desc: Deuterium can be fractionated from liquid hydrogen efficiently by utilizing the high vapor pressure ratio of liquid hydrogen to liquid deuterium at a certain temperature.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Deuterium Fractionation technology. Establish a Fractionator to fractionate deuterium from liquid hydrogen. While the separation efficiency is limited, the production of deuterium signals the approach of a nuclear energy era.

dataArray.Name: Wave Function Interference
dataArray.Desc: Several actions can be taken to cause interference in a particle's wave function by mastering the pattern of probability variations in a quantum jump, which means quantum collapse can be predicted more easily. Utilizing this technology may be more friendly to the cat.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Wave Function Interference technology. Use it to interfere with the wave functions of particles during a quantum jump and induce the quantum collapse that you desire.

dataArray.Name: Miniature Particle Collider
dataArray.Desc: As an expensive but valuable project, the construction of a Small Particle Collider requires advanced materials and a large energy supply.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Small Particle Collider. Use it to produce deuterium and Antimatter efficiently, though it requires a considerable amount of energy.

dataArray.Name: Strange Matter
dataArray.Desc: Strange Matter is a degenerate matter that contains strange quarks from atom nuclei. It is produced by subjecting iron vapor to the enormous energy generated from deuterium-deuterium fusion and compressing iron vapor into a minuscule point.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've obtained Strange Matter. It can warp the space around it, which fulfills the negative energy requirement of warp drives.

dataArray.Name: Artificial Star
dataArray.Desc: A more stable output of the Power Grid generated from matter-Antimatter collisions can be achieved by regulating an Annihilation Constraint Sphere. The technology also demonstrates an energy efficiency that is high enough to produce stable core radiation with wavelengths visible to the human eye, making the reactor a "burning little sun".
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Artificial Sun. Use the power generation facility to efficiently transfer the massive energy from Antimatter Fuel Rods to the Power Grid in a stable and manageable manner.

dataArray.Name: Controlled Annihilation Reaction
dataArray.Desc: When a matter particle collides with an Antimatter particle, its annihilation generates massive energy. The robust utilization of the energy is achieved when the annihilation process is controllable.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the technology for constraining annihilation reactions and achieving stable energy output. Use it to produce Antimatter Fuel Rods.

dataArray.Name: Proliferator Mk.I
dataArray.Desc: Proliferators have transformed the entire production system. When they are sprayed onto products by Spray Coater, extra products or a production speedup effect is gained.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Proliferator MK.I. By using a Spray Coater, Proliferator MK.I can be applied to cargo. This coating will result in extra products or a production speedup effect when the coated cargo is used as raw materials in the production of next-level products.

dataArray.Name: Proliferator Mk.II
dataArray.Desc: Proliferator MK.II is invented with an upgraded formula. This is used to generate more extra products or enhance the production speedup effect.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Proliferator MK.II. Using the Proliferator MK.II to coat cargo can result in a significantly increased production speedup effect or a larger amount of extra products when the coated cargo is used as raw materials for next-level product manufacturing.

dataArray.Name: Proliferator Mk.III
dataArray.Desc: It is clear that using proliferators in industrial production has made a difference. So due to this new understanding, upgrading Proliferators is a high priority. As material technology and manufacturing techniques have improved, the invention of Proliferator MK.III has had a significant effect on product proliferation, though it tightly regulates product line design.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Proliferator MK.III. Using the Proliferator MK.III to coat cargo before using it as raw materials for the next-level product manufacturing will further increase the yield of extra products or the production speedup effect. This shows the importance of ensuring a sufficient supply of raw materials and avoiding cargo overflow.

dataArray.Name: Basic Assembling
dataArray.Desc: A basic assembling machine that integrates traditional mechanical technology to process primary objects into advanced products.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Assembling Machine Mk.I. Use it to process iron ingots, copper ingots and other raw materials into advanced products. Obtain faster Assembling Machine by unlocking technologies.

dataArray.Name: High-Speed Assembling
dataArray.Desc: An upgraded version of the basic assembling machine with improved product manufacturing speeds.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Assembling Machine Mk.II. Use it to increase the processing speed of raw materials and boost the speed of replication by 50%.

dataArray.Name: Quantum Printing
dataArray.Desc: The 3D microscopic structure of particles can be manipulated to maximize manufacturing speed by using Quantum Printing technology.
dataArray.Conclusion: Youâve unlocked the Assembling Machine Mk.III. Use it to increase manufacturing speed by leveraging its integrated Quantum Printing technology to manipulate the particle structure at a more microscopic level. It also increases the speed of replication by 50%.

dataArray.Name: Processor
dataArray.Desc: A large-scale integrated circuit for efficient data processing and processing control.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Processor. Use the large-scale integrated circuit to handle more complex data operations.

dataArray.Name: Quantum Chip
dataArray.Desc: A quantum chip increases the probabilities of particles found in certain states by interfering with the wave functions of particles during a quantum jump in line with the corresponding Rabi oscillations.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Quantum Chip. With a more powerful computing power and an ultra-fast computing speed, Quantum Chips can intelligently identify errors in quantum jump and deploy reverse intervention promptly.

dataArray.Name: Photon Spotlight Mining
dataArray.Desc: In a certain gravitational field, a significant photon-bunching effect can be caused by regulating the propagation of a photon group with positive interference generated by quantum chips in the group's transitions. Such a high-energy laser beam (photon bunch) can instantly cleave a ore vein and convert ores into particles for transportation and encapsulation, which significantly improves the efficiency of mining.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Advanced Mining Machine with easier deployment and improved mining efficiency. Use Conveyor Belts to deliver the collected ores or to enable automatic delivery of ores set as <color="#FD965ECC">"Supply"</color> to Logistics Stations in <color="#FD965ECC">"Demand"</color> by Logistics Drones.

dataArray.Name: Mesoscopic Quantum Entanglement
dataArray.Desc: The massive computing power of quantum chips enables the placement of Strange Matter in specific points, which amplifies the entanglement effect of single quanta to the macromolecular level. With this technology, revolutionizing the traditional chemical engineering industry is easy.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Submicroscopic Quantum Entanglement technology. This will completely replace traditional chemical engineering. Now more advanced chemical plants can be established.

dataArray.Name: Semiconductor Material
dataArray.Desc: Semiconductive microcrystalline components are an ideal material for processor production.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Microcrystalline Component. Use the semiconductor to make more complex integrated circuits.

dataArray.Name: Information Matrix
dataArray.Desc: Instant and effective information transfer can lead to a drastic improvement in industrial production. Obtaining more information technologies by uploading Information Matrices improves the information management of automated production lines.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Information Matrix, a matrix that serves as one of the five source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation. Upload Information Matrices to acquire more information management technologies, which can improve Homebase production efficiency.

dataArray.Name: Automatic Metallurgy
dataArray.Desc: The invention of Arc Smelters has boosted the development of metallurgical technology. A Smelter enhances smelting efficiency with automation.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Arc Smelter. Build Arc Smelters to automatically produce basic materials, such as iron ingots and copper ingots. To achieve full automation, a Sorter is needed to automatically deliver ores from the Conveyor Belt to the Smelter.

dataArray.Name: Smelting Purification
dataArray.Desc: Resulting from recent advances in metallurgy, ore purification technology enables the extraction of high-purity advanced products.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered a more advanced smelting technology. Arc Smelters now can be used for more effective ore purification and the production of higher-purity materials. Smelting stone into silicon is a good option on a planet lacking silicon veins.

dataArray.Name: Crystal Smelting
dataArray.Desc: With a better understanding of lattice structures and advancements in refining technology, a more advanced smelting method for the preparation of high-strength crystals is available.
dataArray.Conclusion: You have acquired expertise in an advanced smelting technology that can rapidly produce diamonds and other advanced materials by modifying the atomic layout of simple substances.

dataArray.Name: Steel Smelting
dataArray.Desc: Smelting iron ingots with a Smelter at very strict and controlled temperatures will improve the products' mechanical properties by altering their crystal forms.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Steel Smelting technology. It is a more advanced method for smelting iron ingots into steel with superior mechanical properties.

dataArray.Name: Thermal Power
dataArray.Desc: A power plant in which the heat energy of combustible fuels is partially converted to energy output.
dataArray.Conclusion: The Thermal Power Plant is now available, a power generation facility that partially converts the heat energy of combustible fuels to electricity.

dataArray.Name: Titanium Smelting
dataArray.Desc: Due to advancements in mining and smelting it has become easier to acquire and control titanium mining and to use it.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Titanium Ore Smelting technology. You can now smelt titanium ores into lightweight and high-density titanium ingots.

dataArray.Name: High-Strength Titanium Alloy
dataArray.Desc: A novel alloy material with improved tensity and durability. Prepared by adding a set formula of alloy elements to titanium during the smelting process, in adherence with the temperature-dependent lattice structure of titanium.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've obtained the Titanium Alloy. This novel alloy material demonstrates better strength and toughness.

dataArray.Name: Reclamation
dataArray.Desc: Extracting soil pile from elevated surfaces for land reclamation facilitates factory construction. Both soil extraction and land reclamation require Foundation.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Foundation. The Foundation is essential for modifying terrains, such as soil extraction from raised surfaces, land reclamation, or returning the altitude to zero.

dataArray.Name: Mini Fusion Power Generation
dataArray.Desc: The newest generation of controlled fusion that enables the creation of compact fusion reactors by using a stellarator to confine static, high-temperature plasma in reactor cores with typical Deuteron Fuel Rods.
dataArray.Conclusion: The Mini Fusion Power Plant is now available. This power generation facility converts energy generated from the controlled deuterium burning in the Deuteron Fuel Rods into electricity.

dataArray.Name: Plane-Filter Smelting
dataArray.Desc: Research shows that a particle flow at a thermodynamically negative temperature can be generated by filtering the quantum states of monopoles with the Wave Function Interference technology. Utilizing this phenomenon will substantially accelerate the smelting or purification of ores.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the <color="#FD965ECC">Plane Smelter</color>. This more advanced smelter has twice the efficiency of an Arc Smelter! However, the <color="#FD965ECC">Unipolar Magnet</color> is required to produce it.

dataArray.Name: Solar Collection
dataArray.Desc: Solar panels only collect a tiny proportion of the sun's electromagnetic radiation energy, so a more efficient method is needed.
dataArray.Conclusion: The Solar Panel is now available. This power generation facility converts solar radiation energy into electrical energy during the day and stores the surplus electricity in Accumulators.

dataArray.Name: Photon Frequency Conversion
dataArray.Desc: A Photon Combiner effectively reduces the losses in solar energy collection by converting low-frequency photons into high-frequency ones.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Photon Combiner. It continuously absorbs low-energy photons to generate a high-energy photon. Try using Grating Crystal to produce it. The process may surprise you.

dataArray.Name: Solar Sail Orbit System
dataArray.Desc: Use <color="#FD965ECC">EM-Rail Ejectors</color> to launch <color="#FD965ECC">Solar Sails</color> on a continuous and massive scale to form a Dyson Swarm for collecting stellar radiation energy more efficiently.
dataArray.Conclusion: The EM-Rail Ejector is now available to powerfully eject Solar Sails to the Dyson Swarm. The limited life span of a Solar Sail can be extended by upgrading technologies.

dataArray.Name: Ray Receiver
dataArray.Desc: The Ray Receiver can receive high-energy rays that are transmitted back from the Dyson Sphere and directly output the energy it has received to the Power Grid. The efficiency of ray reception determines the energy obtained.
dataArray.Conclusion: The Ray Receiver is now available for receiving high-energy rays from the Dyson Sphere and transmitting the received energy to the Power Grid directly.

dataArray.Name: Planetary Ionosphere Utilization
dataArray.Desc: The Planetary Ionosphere Utilization technology gives a Ray Receiver more time for high-energy radiation in a day and night cycle by extending the effective altitude for receiving rays to the outer boundary of the exosphere and increasing their operation times.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Planetary Ionosphere Utilization technology. Consume <color="#FD965ECC">Graviton Lenses</color> to increase the maximum output power of Ray Receivers.

dataArray.Name: Dirac Inversion Mechanism
dataArray.Desc: Revealed by the reverse study on the Dirac equation, proton-antiproton pairs can be easily produced via the collision between vibrating open strings in a critical state that are generated from the concentration of gamma rays. This technology will drastically improve the efficiency of Ray Receivers and convert stellar energy into Antimatter for storage.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Mass-energy Storage technology. The Photon Generation mode of Ray Receivers is now available, and Small Particle Colliders can now invert Critical Photons into Antimatter.

dataArray.Name: Universe Matrix
dataArray.Desc: As an ultimate product of the theory of everything that explains the mystery of the universe, the all-encompassing Universe Matrix reveals the sameness of materials, energy, and information.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Universe Matrix. As an ultimate product of the theory of everything, the all-encompassing matrix explains the ultimate mystery of the universe.

dataArray.Name: Mission Completed!
dataArray.Desc: Congratulations, Builder of the Great Civilization!\r\nYour diligence is rewarded with the completion of the main mission of the Dyson Sphere Program. (The game will continue after completion).
dataArray.Conclusion: Congratulations! Builder of the Great Civilization! Program completed! (You can continue your journey after completion)

dataArray.Name: Energy Storage
dataArray.Desc: Use an <color="#FD965ECC">Accumulator</color> to store surplus power in Power Grid. The Accumulator also helps maintain factory operations by automatically releasing stored power when on-grid power is insufficient.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Energy Storage technology. You can now store surplus power in the Power Grid to Accumulators. Accumulators will automatically discharge electricity when the power supply is insufficient.

dataArray.Name: Interstellar Power Transmission
dataArray.Desc: Use an <color="#FD965ECC">Energy Exchanger</color> to achieve interstellar power transmission by converting surplus power in the Power Grid into fully charged Accumulators and discharging them on another planet from another <color="#FD965ECC">Energy Exchanger</color>.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Energy Exchanger. An Energy Exchanger enables the conversion of surplus power in the Power Grid into full Accumulators, or discharge the electrical power from full Accumulators to supply facilities.

dataArray.Name: Geothermal Extraction
dataArray.Desc: A lava planet is rich in magma with enormous energy, which can be exploited with Geothermal Extraction technology.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Geothermal Extraction technology. Construct Geothermal Power Stations to transform the immense energy from the magma of lava planets into electrical power that can be transmitted to the Power Grid.

dataArray.Name: High-Strength Lightweight Structure
dataArray.Desc: A new high-density, lightweight structure made of Carbon Nanotubes with a higher resistance to stellar gravity than traditional structures.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Frame Material. Due to its excellent resistance to stellar gravity pull, this new high-density, lightweight element is used to produce Dyson Sphere Components that will be then launched onto the Dyson Sphere to form its Nodes and Frames.

dataArray.Name: Vertical Launching Silo
dataArray.Desc: Launch <color="#FD965ECC">Dyson Sphere Components</color> with a <color="#FD965ECC">Small Carrier Rocket</color> to add to the Frames and Nodes of a Dyson Sphere.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Vertical Silo. Build Vertical Silos to launch Small Carrier Rockets that are loaded with Dyson Sphere Components.

dataArray.Name: Dyson Sphere Stress System
dataArray.Desc: The stress distribution on the surface of a Dyson Sphere Node becomes more complex at higher latitudes, so it will be harder to balance the stress system.
dataArray.Conclusion: Youâve increased the maximum latitude of the Dyson Sphere Nodes.

dataArray.Name: Basic Logistics System
dataArray.Desc: Use <color="#FD965ECC">Conveyor Belts</color> and <color="#FD965ECC">Sorters</color> to enable automated production by transporting cargo from one place to another.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Conveyor Belt and the Sorter. Build the two basic facilities for automated logistics to enable automatic delivery of ores stored in Mining Machines to Smelters or Depots.

dataArray.Name: Upgraded Logistics System
dataArray.Desc: A <color="#FD965ECC">Splitter</color> increases the variety of designs of automated transport lines by dividing cargo into multiple batches for easier distribution or by coordinating multiple Conveyor Belts.\r\nUse TAB to switch the style.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Splitter. Use three different patterns of a Splitter to divide cargo into multiple batches for easier sorting or to manage the workload of multiple Conveyor Belts.

dataArray.Name: High-Efficiency Logistics System
dataArray.Desc: Sorter MK.III sorts cargo more effectively, so it is more useful when demand for resources surges.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Conveyor Belt with the greatest carrying capacity, a more efficient Sorter, and Depot with increased capacity.

dataArray.Name: Planetary Logistics System
dataArray.Desc: <color="#FD965ECC">Planet-wide</color> cargo transportation can be achieved through Planetary Logistics Stations and Logistics Drones when the material technology reaches a certain level. With proper configuration of supply tasks, automatic cargo delivery is possible with Logistics Drones.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Planetary Logistics Station and the Logistics Drone. These two basic facilities of the remote logistics system allow Logistics Drones to transport cargo automatically between Logistics Stations according to the configured conditions.

dataArray.Name: Interstellar Logistics System
dataArray.Desc: A giant space elevator for more convenient interstellar material transportation.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Interstellar Logistics Station. This giant space elevator enables interstellar cargo transportation between Logistics Stations across planets via Logistics Vessels.

dataArray.Name: Gas Giants Exploitation
dataArray.Desc: A gas giant is rich in resources, and its mining shows that technology has reached an unprecedented heights.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Orbital Collector. You can use it to extract resources from gas giants. A portion of the extracted fuel is consumed for its operation and maintenance.

dataArray.Name: Integrated Logistics System
dataArray.Desc: With a deeper understanding of material structures, the Integrated Logistics technology has now improved and increased the carrying capacity of Conveyor Belts by combining two successive objects on a Conveyor Belt into one.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Auto-piler and Pile Sorter. By installing an Auto-piler on a Conveyor Belt and ensuring a sufficient power supply, two successive objects on the Conveyor Belt can be integrated into one, significantly increasing the carrying capacity of the Conveyor Belt. After upgrading the Pile Sorter, it can integrate multiple cargos into one and feed out to the Conveyor Belt.

dataArray.Name: Distribution Logistics System
dataArray.Desc: Use Logistics Distributors and Logistics Bots to achieve cargo distribution between Depots or between Depot and Icarus <color="#FD965ECC">on a planet</color>.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Logistics Distributor and the Logistics Bot. Build Logistics Distributors on top of Depots and deploy Logistics Bots to deliver cargo to other Logistics Distributors or Icarus according to the configured conditions.

dataArray.Name: Electromagnetic Drive
dataArray.Desc: Unlock the Electric Motor, the basic component of a power system.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Electric Motor. Use it to accelerate machine operation and to improve the speed of the mecha in the early stage.

dataArray.Name: Magnetic Levitation
dataArray.Desc: An Electromagnetic Turbine generates magnetic force to make objects defy gravity.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Electromagnetic Turbine. Use it to generate magnetic force to levitate objects.

dataArray.Name: Magnetic Particle Trap
dataArray.Desc: This device is developed when material technology reaches a certain level. It can confine particles and cause them to behave in certain ways.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Particle Container. It can be used to immobilize particles at specific locations and induce them to exhibit certain characteristics.

dataArray.Name: Gravitational Wave Refraction
dataArray.Desc: An intricate Graviton Lens made of Strange Matter that is used to distort its peripheral space and refract passing gravitons.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Gravitational Wave Refraction technology. Use Graviton Lenses to build the Space Warper that enables warp flights of the mecha and Logistics Vessels.

dataArray.Name: Gravity Matrix
dataArray.Desc: Gravity Matrices are one of the five basic source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation. Researching them has reconciled the Quantum Field Theory and the General Theory of Relativity.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Gravity Matrix. As one of the five source codes for maintaining the CentreBrain simulation, the matrix has reconciled the Quantum Field Theory and the General Theory of Relativity.

dataArray.Name: Super Magnetic Field Generator
dataArray.Desc: Albeit extremely challenging, the robust creation of a high-intensity artificial magnetic field is the key to the development of other advanced technologies. The mastery of the Super Magnetic Field Excitation technology will prove to be a decisive move in technological development.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've mastered the Super Magnetic Field Excitation technology. Use it to create high-performance materials by inducing atomic-scale lattice distortion in materials.

dataArray.Name: Satellite Power Distribution System
dataArray.Desc: Utilizing the strong magnetic fields stimulated by the super magnetic field ring can transmit electricity over long distances to a wider coverage.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Satellite Substation, which expands the transmission range and increases the power supply coverage.

dataArray.Name: Weapon System
dataArray.Desc: Once weapons appear, the tables are turned. Icarus has what it needs to fight Dark Fog and guard the base, and it can calmly respond to raids as well.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked the Weapon System. Now you can defend your base against raids and survive from the dangers of this universe.

dataArray.Name: Combustible Unit
dataArray.Desc: Coal can release power more efficiently and powerfully after its molecular geometry has been elaborately modified.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked Combustible Units, a highly cost-effective fuel. Further research discovered that this can be used to make shells.

dataArray.Name: Explosive Unit
dataArray.Desc: A classic chemical formula. After reaction conditions and raw material ratios have been optimized, reliable explosives can be made and casually handled.
dataArray.Conclusion: You've unlocked Explosive Units. This efficient and stable explosive can be used to manufacture all types of explosive weapons.

dataArray.Name: Crystal Explosive Unit
